"{\"uid\": \"thegatewaypundit.com-2024-08-second-boxer-male-dna-beats-woman-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Taiwanese boxer Lin Yu-Ting, previously disqualified from the 2023 Women's Boxing World Championships for failing to meet gender eligibility criteria, secured a decisive victory against Uzbekistan's Sitora Turdibekova.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"score\": 0.9999998733515065, \"rank\": 1.0877323249790861e-07, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\"}, {\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-Ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 188, \"end\": 198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.999999998936346, \"rank\": 1.0565015964703599e-09, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The match, which took place on Friday, saw Lin dominate Turdibekova with a 3-0 decision, with each judge scoring every round in favor of Lin.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"NEW-Unbelievable!\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another day at the Paris Olympics and another MAN just pummeled and abused a WOMAN in a boxing match.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Taiwans Lin Yu-Ting, a man who failed a gender test and was barred from competing in the 2023 World Championships, left Uzbekistan's Sitora Turdibekova on the\\u2026pic.twitter.com/7CH8semKmO  - Charlie Kirk (@charliekirk11)August 2, 2024    Lin's win comes after another match, where Italian boxer Angela Carinifaced off against Algerian athlete Imane Khelif, who lasted only 46 seconds.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 494, \"end\": 505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-Ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.999999998936346, \"rank\": 1.0565015964703599e-09, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turning_Point_USA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.363916748867596e-29, \"text\": \"Charlie Kirk\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turning_Point_USA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turning_Point_USA\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9938223410871908, \"rank\": 0.003335054729638439, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9997817472349447, \"rank\": 0.0001986953207258695, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 827, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini was quickly overwhelmed, succumbing to two powerful punches before dropping her helmet and calling the situation \\\"unjust.\\\"\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 870, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999587031535117, \"rank\": 4.129855179465873e-05, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scene escalated as Carini fell to the ground in tears, refusing to shake hands with Khelif.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999587031535117, \"rank\": 4.129855179465873e-05, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin's participation in the Olympics has sparked debate, given her history, similar to Khelif, neither of whom is 'transgender.'\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Both were born women but have XY chromosomes, which are typically associated with male DNA, and were found to have high testosterone levels.\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA has issued a scathing statement aimed at the International Olympic Committee (IOC) concerning its eligibility guidelines for the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA emphasized the importance of maintaining competitive fairness and questioned the IOC's differing regulations, which have allowed Lin and Khelif to compete despite their previous disqualification.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1529, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3423056782434484e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read thefull statementbelow:  As stated, the International Boxing Association (IBA) feels it appropriate at this prevalent time, to address recent media statements regarding those athletes Lin Yu-ting and Imane Khelif, particularly regarding their participation in the Paris Olympic Games 2024.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4144460530801647e-23, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1809, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 1935, \"end\": 1947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We wish tomake the following points in these regards:  On 24 March 2023, IBA disqualified athletes Lin Yu-ting and Imane Khelif from the IBA Women's World Boxing Championships New Delhi 2023.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6877786688067855e-14, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 2202, \"end\": 2211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9995316424710191, \"rank\": 0.0004685701789667639, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This disqualification was a result of their failure to meet the eligibility criteria for participating in the women's competition, as set and laid out in the IBA Regulations.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision, made after a meticulous review, was extremely important and necessary to uphold the level of fairness and utmost integrity of the competition.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Point to note, the athletes did not undergo a testosterone examination but were subject to a separate and recognized test, whereby the specifics remain confidential.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This test conclusively indicated that both athletes did not meet the required necessary eligibility criteria and were found to have competitive advantages over other female competitors.\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision made by IBA on 24 March 2023, was subsequently ratified by the IBA Board of Directors on 25 March 2023.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2926, \"end\": 2929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The official record of this decision can be accessed on the IBA website hereIBA Board of Directors Meeting Minutes.\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3082, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The disqualification was based on two tests conducted on both athletes as follows:  For clarification  Our Committees have rigorously reviewed and endorsed the decision made during the World Championships.\", \"from\": 3139, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While IBA remains committed to ensuring competitive fairness in all of our events, we express concern over the inconsistent application of eligibility criteria by other sporting organizations, including those overseeing the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3351, \"end\": 3354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC's differing regulations on these matters, in which IBA is not involved, raise serious questions about both competitive fairness and athletes' safety.\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3588, \"end\": 3591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3423056782434484e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3643, \"end\": 3646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999968658588843, \"rank\": 3.134132356276684e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For clarification on why the IOC permits athletes with competitive advantages to compete in their events, we urge interested parties to seek answers directly from the IOC.\", \"from\": 3743, \"to\": 3914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3772, \"end\": 3775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3423056782434484e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3910, \"end\": 3913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3423056782434484e-28, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You canemail Jim H\\u1d0fft here, andread more of Jim H\\u1d0fft's articles here.\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign up now and stay ahead in the political landscape.\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4045, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"VisitGatewayHispanic.comto read news of interest to the hispanic community.\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4103, \"end\": 4111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"hispanic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hispanic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"VisitAmericanGulag.orgto learn how to help the prisoners of the protest on January 6th.\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"VisitTGPVideos.comto watch the latest exclusive videos from The Gateway Pundit.\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the mainstream media repeatedly fails and loses public trust, TGP has continued to offer accurate and timely reporting for almost two decades.\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4439, \"entities\": 